Class Grade

java.lang.Object
Grade
public class Grade extends Object
Represents a grade record for a student, including details such as the student ID, course ID, grade, semester, and year. Uses JavaFX properties for binding and observability.

      Constructs a Grade object with the specified student ID, course ID, grade, semester, and year.
      Parameters:
      studentId - the ID of the student
      courseId - the ID of the course
      grade - the grade of the student in the course
      semester - the semester in which the grade was earned
      year - the year in which the grade was earned
